channel.title: FAST Runescape cash!
channel.description:
Well yeah, i'm bored so i'll release my nooby way of making cash on my pures, mains, ect..
Okay, it'd help if you had 100-200k to start with.
Go to the G.E and buy 100 soft clay for max, 19k. 100 law runes for 37k, 100 waters for 1.6k, and 1 air staff for 1.5k.
Now, but a duel ring, and teleport to Cwars, then walk to Yanille.
Look in the Events forum on Runescape forums, and look for a open guilded alter.
Now go to there house and look for a "Lecturn"
It'll give you the option to "study" it, so pick "study."
Now there'll be like 6 different teleport tabs to pick from, i suggest making Falador, just because they sell for 979 in G.E instantly.
After you make 100, sell then repeat. I went from 120k to 1.6m in about 4-6 hours.
Mhm. :cool:
